title: Quick Take: March 15 Primary Results
description: What's next after big wins on March 15 for Hillary Clinton, Donald Trump, and John Kasich. Plus Marco Rubio suspends his campaign. This episode: host/campaign reporter Sam Sanders, campaign reporter Asma Khalid, and political editor Domenico Montanaro. Find the team on Twitter, at nprpolitics.org, or email the show at nprpolitics@npr.org.
